1
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:32,640
Tomorrow,

2
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,519
we'll head back for New Year.

3
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:37,200
Mother turns 60 this year,

4
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:40,680
we'd better bring generous gifts.

5
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,319
And the fifth sister-in-law,

6
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:45,200
she's the legit daughter
of Lord Changxing.

7
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,840
Now she's expecting,

8
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,359
and my brother's been
sent far off to Hanyang.

9
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:51,519
Heard Mother's personally

10
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:54,200
overseeing her every need.

11
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,400
We can't afford to treat her lightly.

12
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,560
I've added 20 percent

13
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,560
on top of the usual gifts.

14
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,680
Mother.

15
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,319
Your cough

16
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:13,159
sounds worse.

17
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,520
It's nothing,

18
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,000
really.

19
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,280
Madam Ji's not going back?

20
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:22,840
She didn't fall asleep

21
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,159
till well past midnight.

22
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,960
She woke up feeling off,

23
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,199
so she's not going.

24
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:28,800
Then I'm not going either.

25
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:31,479
I'll stay and take care of Madam.

26
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,199
Miss, you're truly devoted.

27
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,039
But this is your first time

28
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:36,159
paying New Year's respects there.

29
00:02:36,719 --> 00:02:38,360
You should go no matter what.

30
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,280
The main house

31
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,479
has been urging us

32
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,919
to move back for years,

33
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:50,599
saying family should stay together.

34
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,400
They're merely

35
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:57,000
after Madam's dowry.

36
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:57,800
That's why Madam

37
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,080
won't move back.

38
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,439
Master knows it too.

39
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,360
But the main house's been
nobility for generations,

40
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,759
how could they be short on cash?

41
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:09,240
Big noble families these days

42
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,560
are all show on the outside only.

43
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,680
Nine out of ten are broke.

44
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,919
You'll see when you get there.

45
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,199
Indeed,

46
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,360
we better stay sharp.

47
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,000
No wonder Father

48
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,639
moved out right after the engagement

49
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,879
with the Ji family.

50
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,879
He was already protecting against this.

51
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:33,039
He really plays it smart.

52
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:36,479
People in the capital are all schemers.

53
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:39,000
Madam's too kind,
easy to get taken advantage of.

54
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:40,919
Good thing you came, Miss.

55
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:41,919
With you here,

56
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,199
you can help Madam
make the right decisions.

57
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:28,560
Miss,

58
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:30,000
what a show!

59
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:32,000
Of course.

60
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,360
This is the old family estate

61
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,600
from the late master's time.

62
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,120
Way better than our place.

63
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:37,199
Even Ji Mansion

64
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:38,680
can't match this.

65
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,480
Right, Jinzhao?

66
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,360
Yeah,

67
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,720
even Ji Mansion

68
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,240
wouldn't spend like this.

69
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:47,519
Guess the main house's loaded.

70
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,720
Wait,

71
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,000
Uncle Deyuan is just

72
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,920
a Fourth-Rank Investigating Censor,

73
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,439
where'd all this money come from?

74
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,040
From the main house fortune, of course.

75
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:14,959
Second sister-in-law,

76
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:17,160
my respects to you.

77
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:19,000
Happy new year.

78
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,839
Good day to you, Dezhao.

79
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:24,000
Second Aunt, happy new year.

80
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,639
Happy new year everyone.

81
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:30,639
This must be Jinzhao.

82
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,480
What a beauty.

83
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:36,959
It's cold outside,

84
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,120
let's head in.

85
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:39,839
Come.

86
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:55,079
Happy new year, Mother.

87
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:57,120
Happy new year, Grandma.

88
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,279
Alright get up.

89
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,839
Finally everyone's here.

90
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:15,439
Dezhao.

91
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,600
Jinrong.

92
00:06:16,959 --> 00:06:17,639
Jinxian.

93
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,040
Come to my study,

94
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,120
let's have some tea.

95
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,360
Take a seat.

96
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,279
First time

97
00:06:51,279 --> 00:06:52,720
seeing Jinzhao.

98
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:54,360
She's turned out

99
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,120
so graceful

100
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,759
and gorgeous,

101
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:59,560
like a crabapple bloom.

102
00:07:01,759 --> 00:07:02,560
So it seems

103
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,319
all those rumors outside

104
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,560
were just nonsense.

105
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,120
Have you been betrothed?

106
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,160
Not yet, Grandma.

107
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,279
Not yet?

108
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,399
Didn't you already

109
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,439
have a betrothal

110
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,519
with Lord Liu Siyu's family?

111
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,000
Lian,

112
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,800
don't talk like that.

113
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,480
Jinzhao is older than you,

114
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,759
call her sister.

115
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,199
Lian,

116
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:28,439
you said I was engaged to the Liu family,

117
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,279
how did you know that?

118
00:07:31,079 --> 00:07:32,120
It was Lan,

119
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,360
she wrote it in a letter.

120
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,240
What exactly

121
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,759
did Lan say?

122
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,680
She said

123
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,680
the Liu family came to propose,

124
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,279
but you had your eye on Lord Xian,

125
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:48,199
so you looked down on Liu Xiancheng.

126
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,279
I didn't say that!

127
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,800
That's exactly what you meant.

128
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:54,079
I just said

129
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,199
Jinzhao and Lord Xian

130
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,360
are on good terms.

131
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,839
I never said anything else.

132
00:07:58,399 --> 00:07:59,040
But…
Enough.

133
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,399
The Young Lord

134
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:02,920
is not someone you can gossip about.

135
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,040
Exactly.

136
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:06,439
The Young Lord is far above us.

137
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,639
Any dealings with our family

138
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,759
are only

139
00:08:09,759 --> 00:08:11,079
out of courtesy

140
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:12,439
to the Gu Manor's connections.

141
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,240
As for the Liu family.

142
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:15,560
Lian,

143
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:18,199
Lan only said they came to propose,

144
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,240
not that the match was set.

145
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:21,600
Right?

146
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,040
But…

147
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,079
Yes.

148
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,639
That's right.

149
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,240
A proposal isn't a betrothal.

150
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,519
If every proposal

151
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:36,879
counted as a betrothal,

152
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:37,919
there'd be no end to it.

153
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,200
If this gets out,

154
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,279
it'll look like our family is eager

155
00:08:40,279 --> 00:08:41,519
to marry off daughters.

156
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,519
Lian,

157
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,440
you're still a Gu girl,

158
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:48,519
mind what you say.

159
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,360
And Lan,

160
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:54,639
don't spread things

161
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,440
about me anymore.

162
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:56,799
We may not

163
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:58,159
have grown up together,

164
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,879
but I'm still your sister.

165
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,559
We're family.

166
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:04,440
Even if you don't think for me,

167
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,759
you should think of Father

168
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,279
and the Gu family.

169
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,519
Do you think so?

170
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,679
Yes.

171
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,440
I know I was wrong.

172
00:09:12,039 --> 00:09:12,919
Alright.

173
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,240
We're all family.

174
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:16,320
Talk it out

175
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,559
and it's fine,

176
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,240
nothing serious.

177
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,240
Both Lan

178
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,120
and Jinzhao

179
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,399
are good girls.

180
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:25,600
They'll both

181
00:09:25,879 --> 00:09:27,639
find good matches.

182
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:30,440
Especially Jinzhao.

183
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:35,159
I heard

184
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:36,879
your maternal grandmother

185
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,360
left you all her properties

186
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:39,799
in the capital

187
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,200
as your dowry.

188
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,600
You'll need

189
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,919
a fine husband indeed.

190
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,879
I'll keep an eye out for you as well.

191
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,679
Lian did have a match

192
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,519
with the legit son

193
00:09:53,519 --> 00:09:55,720
of Lord Yao Ping,
Vice Minister of Justice.

194
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,080
Everyone praised it,

195
00:09:58,399 --> 00:09:59,559
said it's a good match.

196
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,240
How did I become the topic?

197
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:06,120
I don't care for this talk.

198
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,360
You all carry on.

199
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:08,759
Lan,
let's go watch the opera.

200
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,559
Alright,

201
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:12,159
all of you, go enjoy the opera.

202
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:13,720
Mother,

203
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:15,919
hasn't arrived yet.

204
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:17,879
Her again.

205
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,519
She's late every time.

206
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,600
It's all your fault.

207
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,960
If I hadn't gone to pick you up,

208
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,120
I wouldn't be late.

209
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:25,639
I only said I was coming,

210
00:10:25,799 --> 00:10:27,080
never asked you to pick me up.

211
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,360
You said you were coming,

212
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,600
how could I not go pick you up?

213
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,679
Young Lord, you're here.

214
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,720
Greetings, Young Lord,

215
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,840
Aunt.

216
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:44,720
Greetings, Ma'am.

217
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,159
Happy New Year.

218
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,960
Happy New Year, Young Lord.

219
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,080
Please sit.

220
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,519
Mother, listen.

221
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,000
We sent someone
to ask before the New Year,

222
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,240
he said he wouldn't come this year.

223
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:01,279
This morning,

224
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:02,639
he suddenly sent word
saying he was coming,

225
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,320
so I had to rush out to pick him up.

226
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,159
He really does change his mind on a whim,

227
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:07,720
making me late.

228
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,159
Your pregnancy is progressing,

229
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:12,399
need to be extra careful.

230
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,279
It doesn't matter being late or not.

231
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,799
Just take it easy.

232
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:20,000
Since everyone's here,

233
00:11:20,519 --> 00:11:21,639
let's go watch the opera.

234
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:22,879
Lian,

235
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,919
look after your sisters.

236
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,360
Especially Jinzhao,

237
00:11:26,759 --> 00:11:28,159
it's her first time here.

238
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:30,639
Me looking after her?

239
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,279
She's older than me,

240
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,519
she doesn't need my care.

241
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,639
Lord Xian,

242
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,759
let's go.

243
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,360
What's the rush?

244
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:42,080
I'm older than you too,

245
00:11:42,559 --> 00:11:43,879
so I don't need your care either.

246
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,200
What's taking so long?

247
00:11:48,399 --> 00:11:49,120
Hurry up!

248
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:52,639
Let's go!

249
00:11:58,919 --> 00:12:00,399
Grandma, I'll stay with you.

250
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,440
I'm going with you.

251
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,279
She's the obedient one.

252
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:09,440
Let's go.

253
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:23,559
You sisters sit here,

254
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,960
chat and laugh a bit,

255
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,240
that's how it should be.

256
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,279
All the operas chosen today

257
00:13:13,279 --> 00:13:14,000
- are good.
- Glad you like them.
I like them all.

258
00:13:18,399 --> 00:13:19,080
Good.

259
00:13:52,279 --> 00:13:53,000
What are you doing?

260
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,159
Still looking?

261
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,840
Go take a closer look then.

262
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,600
Stop talking nonsense!

263
00:13:59,519 --> 00:14:00,399
Don't think

264
00:14:00,399 --> 00:14:01,480
I don't know what you're thinking.

265
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:03,759
Jinzhao has a thing for him?

266
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,840
I think you're the one who's interested.

267
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:09,200
Think about

268
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,080
his status.

269
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,919
Even I don't dare think too much.

270
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,799
You really are bold.

271
00:14:16,519 --> 00:14:18,000
I'm not thinking anything.

272
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,440
I just

273
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,720
think he looks good

274
00:14:21,039 --> 00:14:22,120
and took a few extra glances.

275
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,759
He really does look good.

276
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:32,519
But that temper of his,

277
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:33,559
better not test it.

278
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,240
Don't know

279
00:14:36,399 --> 00:14:38,120
what he sees in Jinzhao,

280
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:39,600
he actually pays more attention to her.

281
00:14:42,159 --> 00:14:42,960
My Father said

282
00:14:43,159 --> 00:14:44,720
Jinzhao even dares to talk back

283
00:14:44,879 --> 00:14:46,159
to Uncle Dezhao
in front of outsiders.

284
00:14:46,399 --> 00:14:47,080
Is that true?

285
00:14:47,519 --> 00:14:48,519
Don't even bring it up!

286
00:14:48,799 --> 00:14:49,960
Ever since she came back,

287
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:51,440
my life's been hard!

288
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,919
Even wanting an extra dish,

289
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:53,960
I have to go to the kitchen

290
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,679
and pay extra to get it.

291
00:14:57,399 --> 00:14:58,799
And you just put up with it?

292
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,399
What else can I do?

293
00:15:00,559 --> 00:15:01,559
She's the legit daughter,

294
00:15:01,799 --> 00:15:02,639
what am I?

295
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:05,000
So what if she's the legit daughter?

296
00:15:05,519 --> 00:15:06,759
I'm a legit daughter too!

297
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,919
I've never bullied anyone.

298
00:15:21,399 --> 00:15:22,840
Do you know what Cao Cao's

299
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,519
two biggest mistakes in his life were?

300
00:15:29,519 --> 00:15:31,360
One was mistakenly executing Cai Mao,

301
00:15:31,519 --> 00:15:32,879
the other was letting Guan Yu go.

302
00:15:34,159 --> 00:15:35,600
Cai Mao should've been put to good use.

303
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:36,960
But Guan Yu

304
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:38,960
should've been killed.

305
00:15:41,399 --> 00:15:42,440
Don't you agree?

306
00:15:45,519 --> 00:15:46,200
Second Aunt,

307
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,919
this opera is really good.

308
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,240
Which troupe is it from?

309
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:51,320
It's the Spring Grass Troupe
from south of the city.

310
00:16:11,399 --> 00:16:13,279
This is truly outrageous!

311
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:21,759
I need to change clothes.

312
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:23,240
Miss, this way please.

313
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,759
I need to change too.

314
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:43,720
Wait a moment!

315
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:44,960
Let's go together

316
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,320
after this act.

317
00:17:02,519 --> 00:17:03,399
Running away without a fight,

318
00:17:03,679 --> 00:17:04,440
doesn't suit you.

319
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:08,359
Can you stop following me?

320
00:17:10,039 --> 00:17:11,079
Your handkerchief…

321
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:11,839
Young Lord,

322
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:12,960
I can't afford to offend you!

323
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,359
And I don't want another whipping!

324
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,599
Please just let me go,
can you?

325
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:18,680
You can't afford to offend me,

326
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,359
so you can afford Chen Yanyun?

327
00:17:22,759 --> 00:17:23,680
What did you say?

328
00:17:24,799 --> 00:17:25,720
Don't talk nonsense!

329
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,200
Nonsense?

330
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,680
New Year's Eve, City God Temple festival,

331
00:17:30,359 --> 00:17:31,680
I saw it myself

332
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,559
that Chen guy

333
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,319
jumped into the river to save you.

334
00:17:35,839 --> 00:17:36,759
That never happened!

335
00:17:37,519 --> 00:17:38,720
You're spreading rumors!

336
00:17:39,519 --> 00:17:40,359
If I'm spreading rumors,

337
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,559
may I be struck by lightning.

338
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,160
And if you're lying,

339
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,440
you too.

340
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,200
Meeting you already

341
00:17:46,599 --> 00:17:48,119
feels like I've been struck by lightning!

342
00:17:49,839 --> 00:17:50,599
There's a higher spot,

343
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,240
go stand there and say it if you dare!

344
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,440
You think I won't?

345
00:17:54,839 --> 00:17:55,960
Of course you dare!

346
00:17:56,599 --> 00:17:57,640
You'd dare anything!

347
00:17:57,799 --> 00:17:58,480
You are

348
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,880
the noble Young Lord!

349
00:18:00,039 --> 00:18:01,400
What wouldn't you dare?

350
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,000
What are people like us

351
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,440
worth in your eyes?

352
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:05,680
You just say

353
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,400
and do whatever you want!

354
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,559
Gu Jinzhao,

355
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:08,640
you've gone too far!

356
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:09,839
So what if I have?

357
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,240
Kill me if you can!

358
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:11,799
You…

359
00:18:24,119 --> 00:18:25,720
You ungrateful thing!

360
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:28,640
If I weren't considering

361
00:18:29,039 --> 00:18:30,359
you once saved my life…

362
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:36,559
Xian, Jinzhao.

363
00:18:36,799 --> 00:18:37,720
Aunt.

364
00:18:40,119 --> 00:18:41,319
What are you two doing here?

365
00:18:44,279 --> 00:18:45,079
Her handkerchief fell,

366
00:18:45,519 --> 00:18:46,440
I picked it up for her.

367
00:18:47,279 --> 00:18:48,119
I'm returning it now.

368
00:18:50,319 --> 00:18:51,400
Young Lord is mistaken,

369
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,799
this isn't mine.

370
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:55,400
I clearly saw it was yours!

371
00:18:55,519 --> 00:18:56,759
How can you lie like that?

372
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,079
How is it not yours?

373
00:18:58,279 --> 00:18:59,440
How could I not

374
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,720
recognize my own thing?

375
00:19:03,359 --> 00:19:04,359
It's cold in the courtyard,

376
00:19:05,079 --> 00:19:06,519
I'll take my leave, Aunt,

377
00:19:06,519 --> 00:19:07,400
Young Lord.

378
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:08,359
I was going to go

379
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:09,640
get my hand warmer anyway.

380
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,599
Gu Jinzhao!

381
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,640
Enough.

382
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,720
She said it's not hers.

383
00:19:16,839 --> 00:19:17,480
Are you going

384
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,559
to force her to take it?

385
00:19:19,279 --> 00:19:20,200
What handkerchief?

386
00:19:20,519 --> 00:19:21,119
Give it to me.

387
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:23,680
Why would I give it to you?

388
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,319
I picked it up.

389
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:28,519
Where are you going?
The feast is about to start!

390
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,000
All grown up now,

391
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,359
still no sense of propriety.

392
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:33,720
Miss,

393
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,720
but Young Lord's already of age.

394
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,000
Yes,

395
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:38,200
he's of age.

396
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,079
That's not fair!
You are two people!

397
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,599
Ma'am,

398
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,680
ladies,

399
00:19:58,720 --> 00:19:59,519
young masters!

400
00:19:59,519 --> 00:20:00,759
The snacks are here!

401
00:20:02,559 --> 00:20:03,720
- 30,000 coins.
- Snacks are here!

402
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:25,039
The handkerchief's still with Xian.

403
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,640
If he goes crazy

404
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,680
and takes it out,

405
00:20:27,839 --> 00:20:29,240
and someone notices

406
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,599
my stitching matches it,

407
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:31,640
I'm in trouble.

408
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:33,240
You're all set, right?

409
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:36,920
Nicely done!

410
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,279
Lan's lotus

411
00:20:40,279 --> 00:20:41,319
is well done too.

412
00:20:42,960 --> 00:20:43,759
Jinzhao.

413
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,359
What's wrong?

414
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:47,880
Second Aunt,

415
00:20:48,079 --> 00:20:49,240
my embroidery isn't good,

416
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:50,440
not worth showing.

417
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,039
It's fine.

418
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,559
Ma'am just likes

419
00:20:54,839 --> 00:20:56,759
girls doing needlework.

420
00:20:57,079 --> 00:20:58,480
So we're all just

421
00:20:58,759 --> 00:21:00,119
keeping her entertained.

422
00:21:00,519 --> 00:21:01,519
Don't take it seriously.

423
00:21:01,799 --> 00:21:03,000
Thank you for the advice, Second Aunt.

424
00:21:03,759 --> 00:21:04,799
Second Madam, please come quick!

425
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:06,839
Coming!

426
00:21:07,599 --> 00:21:08,599
Keep stitching.

427
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:15,440
Lan,

428
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,079
how is

429
00:21:17,240 --> 00:21:18,920
your lotus so good?

430
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:21,279
I just learned a bit from my mother.

431
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,960
Your mother's that good too?

432
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,640
Isn't she from a merchant family?

433
00:21:26,839 --> 00:21:27,519
Oh right,

434
00:21:27,759 --> 00:21:29,400
you mean "mother".

435
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,359
- Uncle.
- What are you looking at?
Try this pastry.

436
00:21:35,799 --> 00:21:36,799
Just because of my

437
00:21:36,799 --> 00:21:37,960
"merchant's daughter" comment?

438
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:38,519
[Jinxian,]
[your turn!]

439
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:40,799
Did it hit your nerve too?

440
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:48,480
Why are you shaking your head?

441
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:49,839
You people

442
00:21:49,839 --> 00:21:50,920
from merchant families

443
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,640
are always so petty!

444
00:21:52,839 --> 00:21:53,480
Say it

445
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:55,039
if you've got the guts.

446
00:21:56,079 --> 00:21:57,839
Since you act so high and mighty,

447
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,240
why are you wearing

448
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:01,000
a fake gold cicada hairpin?

449
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:04,759
What did you say?

450
00:22:05,079 --> 00:22:06,359
Fake?

451
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:08,119
Then I'll say it straight.

452
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:10,240
This gold cicada hairpin

453
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:11,680
is this autumn's design

454
00:22:11,799 --> 00:22:13,079
from my maternal family's jewelry shop.

455
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,559
Just that cicada alone

456
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:16,200
used three taels of gold.

457
00:22:16,839 --> 00:22:18,000
If I'm not mistaken,

458
00:22:18,319 --> 00:22:19,599
the one you're wearing

459
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:21,359
is hollow, gold-plated.

460
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:22,759
Don't believe me? Look,

461
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:24,880
the gold on the sides

462
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:25,839
is already worn off.

463
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,839
Nonsense!

464
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:31,599
Nonsense or not,

465
00:22:31,599 --> 00:22:33,039
you know in your heart.

466
00:22:33,119 --> 00:22:34,759
If you want proof,

467
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,640
take it off

468
00:22:37,039 --> 00:22:37,839
and drop it in water.

469
00:22:38,559 --> 00:22:40,480
If it floats,

470
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:42,039
that'd be something.

471
00:22:46,759 --> 00:22:47,559
Girls,

472
00:22:49,759 --> 00:22:50,799
how's the embroidery?

473
00:22:52,079 --> 00:22:52,960
Grandma.

474
00:22:55,799 --> 00:22:56,759
This lotus

475
00:22:57,079 --> 00:22:58,599
looks almost alive.

476
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,319
You must

477
00:23:00,519 --> 00:23:01,640
have practiced a lot.

478
00:23:02,359 --> 00:23:03,359
Thank you, Grandma.

479
00:23:03,839 --> 00:23:04,680
A koi?

480
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,440
A bit weaker than the lotus.

481
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:10,279
Grandma!

482
00:23:11,519 --> 00:23:12,400
Still not bad.

483
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:15,160
How's Jinzhao's work?

484
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,519
Let me have a look.

485
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,319
Grandma,

486
00:23:17,559 --> 00:23:18,960
my skills are poor,

487
00:23:19,359 --> 00:23:20,359
it's not well done.

488
00:23:22,039 --> 00:23:23,039
Even if it's not good,

489
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:24,720
you can still show it!

490
00:23:26,519 --> 00:23:27,599
No way, Jinzhao,

491
00:23:28,279 --> 00:23:28,599
this…

492
00:23:28,839 --> 00:23:30,119
did you really make it?

493
00:23:33,039 --> 00:23:34,640
What's this supposed to be?

494
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:35,559
Look at this!

495
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:38,119
This…

496
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:40,319
This is…

497
00:23:41,079 --> 00:23:42,240
It's a butterfly.

498
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:43,960
A butterfly?

499
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:44,839
I thought

500
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:46,319
it was a moth!

501
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:48,160
What,
your mother

502
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,119
never taught you needlework?

503
00:23:52,279 --> 00:23:53,000
Oh right,

504
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:54,920
you were kicked out as a child

505
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,680
and raised by your grandmother.

506
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:01,599
I heard the Ji family
is the richest in Tongzhou.

507
00:24:01,799 --> 00:24:02,640
Well,

508
00:24:03,039 --> 00:24:03,759
what's the point
of a big dowry?

509
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:06,039
Proper upbringing still matters.

510
00:24:06,039 --> 00:24:06,559
It's Jinzhao's.

511
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:07,960
With skills like that,

512
00:24:08,119 --> 00:24:09,160
how will you face

513
00:24:09,279 --> 00:24:10,200
your in-laws later?

514
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:11,680
Lian,

515
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:14,319
the Ji family in Tongzhou are your elders,

516
00:24:14,759 --> 00:24:16,240
how can you talk like that?

517
00:24:16,839 --> 00:24:17,440
Exactly.

518
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,039
My poor skills are on me,

519
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,400
what does it have
to do with my grandparents?

520
00:24:21,279 --> 00:24:21,880
Right.

521
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,960
That wasn't fair, Lian.

522
00:24:24,519 --> 00:24:25,680
I heard

523
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:26,559
Mrs. Ji

524
00:24:26,559 --> 00:24:28,160
hired Ms. Xue

525
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:29,799
from Silken Pavilion

526
00:24:29,799 --> 00:24:30,640
just to teach

527
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:32,079
her needlework.

528
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:33,759
Then why

529
00:24:33,759 --> 00:24:35,200
is it so crude?

530
00:24:35,559 --> 00:24:37,279
Is that all Silken Pavilion can teach?

531
00:24:38,559 --> 00:24:40,599
Maybe you're new here,

532
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:41,640
just playing it down, right?

533
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:43,359
We're all family,

534
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:44,720
no need to be so modest.

535
00:24:45,559 --> 00:24:46,440
I happen to have

536
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:48,200
a handkerchief she embroidered herself.

537
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:49,720
You'll see once you look.

538
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:53,480
Mother,

539
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,599
look!

540
00:24:54,799 --> 00:24:56,160
This orchid,

541
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:58,119
both form and spirit are perfect!

542
00:24:59,119 --> 00:25:00,680
So lifelike.

543
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,359
What's that she stitched?

544
00:25:02,599 --> 00:25:03,319
Let me see.

545
00:25:06,839 --> 00:25:07,880
Jinzhao stitched it.

546
00:25:15,759 --> 00:25:16,880
It's really well done.

547
00:25:17,799 --> 00:25:18,480
Jinzhao,

548
00:25:19,039 --> 00:25:21,079
did you really embroider this?

549
00:25:23,519 --> 00:25:24,279
Yes.

550
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:33,559
My luck's
great today!

551
00:25:37,599 --> 00:25:38,359
Jinzhao.

552
00:25:40,759 --> 00:25:41,400
Jinxian,

553
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:42,480
I need to speak

554
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:43,839
to the Young Lord alone.

555
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,319
Okay, I'll leave you to chat.

556
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:50,440
Mad?

557
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:53,079
Mad I made you admit

558
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,640
the handkerchief was yours?

559
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:57,599
Get this straight,

560
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,440
I was helping you.

561
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,960
Thanks for the help, Young Lord.

562
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:04,400
Next time, please don't.

563
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,079
So I was wrong?

564
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:08,359
You gave my handkerchief
to Lan,

565
00:26:09,599 --> 00:26:10,480
what do you think she'll think?

566
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:11,839
So that's what you're worried about?

567
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:14,160
She won't say anything.

568
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,880
How do you know she won't?

569
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:18,920
When I speak,

570
00:26:19,279 --> 00:26:19,839
who dares not listen,

571
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,240
besides you?

572
00:26:22,359 --> 00:26:23,359
What about Aunt?

573
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,240
She was there.

574
00:26:25,799 --> 00:26:26,720
She saw
what happened.

575
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:28,759
Jinzhao,

576
00:26:28,759 --> 00:26:29,920
why are you so fussy?

577
00:26:30,079 --> 00:26:31,039
What are you afraid of?

578
00:26:31,279 --> 00:26:32,240
She's my sister!

579
00:26:34,119 --> 00:26:35,480
You wouldn't understand.

580
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,640
Jinzhao, where are you going?

581
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:56,480
Slow down.

582
00:27:23,359 --> 00:27:24,440
Everything has its fate.

583
00:27:25,079 --> 00:27:25,720
This cat

584
00:27:26,119 --> 00:27:27,039
was probably bitten
in a fight.

585
00:27:28,359 --> 00:27:29,079
It won't live long.

586
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,440
Saving it now

587
00:27:31,839 --> 00:27:32,519
will only make it
suffer more.

588
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,200
So by your logic,

589
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,319
I shouldn't have saved you

590
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,279
at Blessed Fane either.

591
00:27:38,279 --> 00:27:39,880
You've got your own fate anyway.

592
00:27:54,119 --> 00:27:55,279
Do you want to save it

593
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:57,000
or put it out of its misery?

594
00:28:30,440 --> 00:28:30,920
My lord.

595
00:28:51,279 --> 00:28:52,160
What are you staring at?

596
00:28:52,839 --> 00:28:54,000
Always causing me trouble.

597
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,480
Didn't expect you

598
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:57,119
to be so patient with a cat,

599
00:28:57,519 --> 00:28:58,920
yet so cruel to people.

600
00:29:00,519 --> 00:29:01,440
You've got a death wish?

601
00:29:02,079 --> 00:29:03,640
Want another whipping?

602
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:07,440
Looks like you really resent me.

603
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,160
Wouldn't you?

604
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,680
I didn't provoke you at all

605
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:11,759
and still got whipped.

606
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,480
And that Mr. Zhang.

607
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,480
He fell seriously ill

608
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:16,920
just because of your prank.

609
00:29:17,279 --> 00:29:18,279
He's totally innocent!

610
00:29:19,519 --> 00:29:20,359
He's innocent?

611
00:29:20,559 --> 00:29:21,400
I'm the innocent one!

612
00:29:21,799 --> 00:29:22,559
If you hadn't

613
00:29:22,559 --> 00:29:23,599
stood me up for no reason,

614
00:29:24,359 --> 00:29:25,680
why would I lose my temper?

615
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:27,079
Stood you up?

616
00:29:27,559 --> 00:29:28,799
When did I ever do that?

617
00:29:29,839 --> 00:29:30,839
Playing dumb?

618
00:29:31,559 --> 00:29:32,720
I sent you an invitation

619
00:29:33,799 --> 00:29:35,039
and you snubbed me.

620
00:29:35,839 --> 00:29:36,519
What,

621
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:38,640
was I supposed to tolerate that?

622
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:39,920
Invitation?

623
00:29:40,559 --> 00:29:42,200
I never got anything.

624
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,680
Xianhuai.

625
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:57,599
So,
the handkerchief

626
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,880
was given to the Young Lord
by Ms. Jinzhao?

627
00:30:00,279 --> 00:30:00,599
Then…

628
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:04,160
Wouldn't that be a private exchange?

629
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:05,599
It's not her first time

630
00:30:05,599 --> 00:30:06,640
doing that.

631
00:30:21,279 --> 00:30:22,240
Jinzhao, you're here.

632
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,480
Still up so late?

633
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,240
Come in.

634
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:26,359
I came to thank you

635
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,319
for speaking up for me.

636
00:30:29,559 --> 00:30:30,480
You mean
the embroidery thing?

637
00:30:31,519 --> 00:30:32,839
We're sisters.

638
00:30:33,039 --> 00:30:34,599
They were mocking your grandmother,

639
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:35,960
of course I'd defend you.

640
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,079
So I won't pursue

641
00:30:38,079 --> 00:30:39,680
you hiding Ye Xian's invitation

642
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,160
from me.

643
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,160
What invitation?

644
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:48,720
Well,

645
00:30:49,039 --> 00:30:50,279
whether Ye Xian pursues it,

646
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,359
that's another matter.

647
00:30:52,200 --> 00:30:53,440
What are you talking about?

648
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:58,319
When I first returned,

649
00:30:58,519 --> 00:31:00,160
you had no issue with me.

650
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:01,279
I…

651
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:03,319
I suppose lately

652
00:31:03,319 --> 00:31:04,480
things have changed in the house.

653
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:05,799
Because of me,

654
00:31:06,079 --> 00:31:08,000
Concubine Song took some losses.

655
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,720
So you resent me.

656
00:31:10,839 --> 00:31:12,039
You think my return

657
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,039
got in your way.

658
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:16,160
I've never thought that.

659
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:19,119
I'm a straightforward person.

660
00:31:20,279 --> 00:31:21,240
Yes, I'm the legit daughter

661
00:31:21,359 --> 00:31:22,079
and you're not.

662
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:24,039
But since I was a baby,

663
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:25,640
I grew up at my grandmother's.

664
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:27,240
I never lived a day
as a true legit daughter.

665
00:31:28,519 --> 00:31:29,039
And you,

666
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,480
since birth,

667
00:31:30,799 --> 00:31:32,319
you were the only miss in the house.

668
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:33,920
Not legit,

669
00:31:34,319 --> 00:31:35,559
yet treated like one.

670
00:31:36,119 --> 00:31:37,400
What I'm saying

671
00:31:37,759 --> 00:31:38,680
is just to tell you

672
00:31:39,759 --> 00:31:41,640
that in my eyes there's no such divide.

673
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:44,039
You don't need to see me as a rival.

674
00:31:46,079 --> 00:31:47,079
Jinzhao, that's really unfair

675
00:31:47,079 --> 00:31:48,400
of you to say.

676
00:31:49,359 --> 00:31:50,680
How am I supposed to take that?

677
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,200
I've said my piece.

678
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:56,000
If you take it in, good.

679
00:31:56,319 --> 00:31:57,359
If not,

680
00:31:57,599 --> 00:31:58,519
and you keep stirring trouble,

681
00:31:59,160 --> 00:31:59,920
I'm not the type

682
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,079
to repay evil with kindness.

683
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:03,240
Qingpu, let's go.

684
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:10,039
So fake and pretentious!

685
00:32:10,759 --> 00:32:12,119
I don't believe
that if roles were reversed,

686
00:32:12,279 --> 00:32:13,599
she could still be so detached!

687
00:32:14,079 --> 00:32:14,960
Just talking big
without feeling it herself.

688
00:32:17,559 --> 00:32:18,000
Let's go!

689
00:32:25,279 --> 00:32:26,160
[Didn't expect you]

690
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,839
[to be so patient with a cat,]

691
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,599
[yet so cruel to people.]

692
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:36,119
Miss.

693
00:32:37,799 --> 00:32:38,440
Sis.

694
00:32:39,559 --> 00:32:40,640
What are you doing outside?

695
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,039
Aren't you cold?

696
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:43,839
Cold is good,
keeps the mind clear.

697
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,079
Always full of strange ideas.

698
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:49,240
You're afraid of the cold,

699
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,720
I'll help you inside.

700
00:32:55,559 --> 00:32:56,119
Sis,
please sit.

701
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:05,960
Before the New Year,
I attended a banquet

702
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:06,960
for Lord Wuning's birthday banquet,

703
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,680
and ran into Viscount Weiyuan's wife.

704
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:09,799
Only then did I know

705
00:33:09,799 --> 00:33:11,240
their second son is already engaged

706
00:33:11,440 --> 00:33:12,119
to the youngest daughter

707
00:33:12,119 --> 00:33:13,240
of Lord Wuning,

708
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:14,400
Qiu Fang.

709
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:16,880
I remember he's about your age,

710
00:33:17,279 --> 00:33:18,799
maybe even a few months younger.

711
00:33:19,759 --> 00:33:20,680
To be honest,

712
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:23,279
mother also mentioned your marriage.

713
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:24,920
I said,

714
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:27,119
Xian's always had
his own ideas since childhood,

715
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,119
so this

716
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,880
should be his decision.

717
00:33:30,279 --> 00:33:31,160
Do you think so?

718
00:33:33,079 --> 00:33:33,920
Why are you laughing?

719
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,400
I'm just laughing

720
00:33:37,599 --> 00:33:39,000
that you always like

721
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,319
to beat around the bush.

722
00:33:41,279 --> 00:33:42,319
Doesn't it get tiring?

723
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:43,559
Fine,

724
00:33:44,039 --> 00:33:45,160
I'll be direct then.

725
00:33:46,799 --> 00:33:47,920
You're of age now,

726
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:49,359
and you're the only heir of the family.

727
00:33:50,039 --> 00:33:51,759
Mother and father plan

728
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:53,160
to start looking for a match this spring.

729
00:33:53,519 --> 00:33:54,759
Get married early,

730
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:56,119
so you can carry on

731
00:33:56,119 --> 00:33:57,039
the family line.

732
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:00,279
Yeah.

733
00:34:00,839 --> 00:34:02,039
Even if I die early,

734
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:03,759
you'll all feel more at ease, right?

735
00:34:04,079 --> 00:34:05,240
What are you saying?

736
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:08,480
Since you care so much
about continuing the family line,

737
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,119
go have your own children.

738
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:11,679
Even letting your husband

739
00:34:11,679 --> 00:34:12,840
take concubines is fine.

740
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:14,519
Why drag me into it?

741
00:34:15,039 --> 00:34:16,119
I can't handle you anymore?

742
00:34:23,559 --> 00:34:24,559
You wouldn't happen

743
00:34:25,039 --> 00:34:26,760
to like a Gu girl, would you?

744
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:33,760
Is it that Jinzhao?

745
00:34:36,679 --> 00:34:37,599
So what if it is?

746
00:34:38,719 --> 00:34:39,480
And what if it isn't?

747
00:34:39,639 --> 00:34:40,679
If it isn't, good.

748
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:42,039
If it is,

749
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:42,920
then I advise you,

750
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,119
forget it early.

751
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,360
You're the heir,

752
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:46,519
destined to inherit

753
00:34:46,519 --> 00:34:47,719
the entire Marquis Manor.

754
00:34:48,159 --> 00:34:48,960
A girl from the Gu family,

755
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,239
let alone Jinzhao,

756
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:51,199
even Lian wouldn't be

757
00:34:51,199 --> 00:34:52,280
a match for you.

758
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:54,280
I shouldn't have

759
00:34:54,559 --> 00:34:55,280
let you stay

760
00:34:55,280 --> 00:34:56,400
at the Gu Manor so often.

761
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:58,880
All these girls

762
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:00,119
have only caused unnecessary trouble.

763
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:02,519
I'll keep this

764
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:04,000
from our parents for now.

765
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,679
But you'd better know it.

766
00:35:06,159 --> 00:35:07,400
If father and mother find out,

767
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,519
you know what the consequences will be.

768
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:10,119
If you truly care for her,

769
00:35:10,239 --> 00:35:11,280
you should cut those feelings off

770
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,079
early.

771
00:35:14,119 --> 00:35:14,960
Xianhuai!

772
00:35:17,599 --> 00:35:18,159
Miss.

773
00:35:18,519 --> 00:35:19,880
Go pack the Young Lord's things,

774
00:35:20,119 --> 00:35:20,920
he's returning to Marquis Manor.

775
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:22,920
This…

776
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:23,920
What,

777
00:35:24,199 --> 00:35:25,719
do my words not carry weight anymore?

778
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:26,519
I wouldn't dare.
I'll…

779
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:28,880
go pack now.

780
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:46,159
People always say gold and silver

781
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,639
can't compare to something made by hand.

782
00:35:48,519 --> 00:35:49,719
Giving these to Mr. Chen,

783
00:35:50,039 --> 00:35:50,920
let alone him,

784
00:35:51,239 --> 00:35:52,400
I even find it tacky.

785
00:35:54,199 --> 00:35:55,519
[Mr. Jinrong's here!]

786
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,320
Greetings, Jinzhao.

787
00:36:02,719 --> 00:36:04,400
You're…

788
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:07,400
Just picking out a few suitable gifts

789
00:36:07,639 --> 00:36:09,079
for some social visits.

790
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:14,719
Jinrong,

791
00:36:15,119 --> 00:36:16,000
what is it?

792
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:17,559
Here's the thing.

793
00:36:18,599 --> 00:36:19,719
A while ago,

794
00:36:19,719 --> 00:36:21,159
I went to Yong'an Bridge

795
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,800
and accidentally saw you

796
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:23,880
with Mr. Chen's nephew,

797
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:24,639
Chen Xuanqing.

798
00:36:27,679 --> 00:36:28,719
Well, don't misunderstand.

799
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,599
I saw it,

800
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:31,760
but I won't spread it.

801
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:33,159
Not even

802
00:36:33,159 --> 00:36:34,119
to father and mother.

803
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:35,360
Don't worry.

804
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:41,400
A few days ago,

805
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,880
you wanted to borrow 200 taels from me,

806
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:46,239
I've got it ready.

807
00:36:46,679 --> 00:36:47,199
Well…

808
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,239
Thank you, Jinzhao!

809
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,320
But,

810
00:36:52,599 --> 00:36:54,400
since it's a loan, there are rules.

811
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:56,320
Even between siblings,

812
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:59,239
we still need signatures and fingerprints.

813
00:36:59,719 --> 00:37:01,159
Of course.

814
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:04,039
Borrowed: 200 taels.

815
00:37:04,639 --> 00:37:05,440
Any collateral?

816
00:37:06,119 --> 00:37:07,199
I…

817
00:37:09,639 --> 00:37:10,920
If you don't have anything suitable,

818
00:37:11,159 --> 00:37:12,000
the jade bracelet

819
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,519
you gave me that day will do, alright?

820
00:37:14,239 --> 00:37:14,800
Alright!

821
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:17,719
You really are straightforward.

822
00:37:28,519 --> 00:37:30,039
Six-month term,

823
00:37:30,119 --> 00:37:32,440
with three months' interest
added upon maturity…

824
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:35,159
This…

825
00:37:35,679 --> 00:37:36,920
This is "9 out, 13 return"?

826
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,159
Jinzhao, you…
I didn't expect you

827
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:40,239
to know pawnshop rules so well,

828
00:37:40,559 --> 00:37:42,079
even that kind of loan sharking math.

829
00:37:45,159 --> 00:37:45,639
Well,

830
00:37:46,519 --> 00:37:47,840
at that rate,

831
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:49,199
I'm afraid I won't be able to pay it back.

832
00:37:51,039 --> 00:37:52,199
Are you out of your mind?

833
00:37:52,559 --> 00:37:54,360
That jade bracelet was
a gift from you anyway.

834
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:55,679
Even if you can't repay it,

835
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:56,679
what's there to fear?

836
00:37:58,639 --> 00:37:59,320
Oh, right!

837
00:37:59,639 --> 00:38:00,440
I really was being silly.

838
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,159
Thank you, Jinzhao.
Alright.

839
00:38:05,519 --> 00:38:06,639
If no objections,

840
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:07,960
just sign and press your seal.

841
00:38:08,599 --> 00:38:09,119
Okay.

842
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,079
Same handwriting,

843
00:38:36,199 --> 00:38:37,400
same fingerprint.

844
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:40,559
This pawn ticket

845
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:41,719
really is yours.
This…

846
00:38:42,519 --> 00:38:43,000
You…

847
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:44,480
Wait,

848
00:38:45,199 --> 00:38:46,039
I specifically skipped

849
00:38:46,039 --> 00:38:47,079
Ji's pawnshop

850
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,280
and went to He's,

851
00:38:48,480 --> 00:38:49,039
how did you…

852
00:38:49,039 --> 00:38:50,119
You didn't know.

853
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,360
He's Pawnshop

854
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:52,800
also has a 30% share from the Ji family.

855
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,199
An official kiln vase

856
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:58,079
and a jade ring,

857
00:38:58,599 --> 00:38:59,920
valued at 150 taels.

858
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,400
What do you need so much silver for?

859
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:06,480
Is it also for your classmate's sister's

860
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,480
dowry?

861
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,360
This is…

862
00:39:10,079 --> 00:39:10,679
Say it!

863
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:12,559
What are you borrowing so much money for?

864
00:39:13,119 --> 00:39:14,519
You've even learned to pawn things now!

865
00:39:15,519 --> 00:39:16,599
If you lie,

866
00:39:16,679 --> 00:39:17,639
I'll take this ticket

867
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:18,920
straight to mother

868
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,159
or even father!
No!

869
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,039
Jinzhao,

870
00:39:22,039 --> 00:39:23,440
please don't tell them!

871
00:39:24,199 --> 00:39:25,199
I'll tell you.

872
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:29,760
Actually…

873
00:39:30,199 --> 00:39:31,639
It was the month before last,

874
00:39:32,119 --> 00:39:33,840
a classmate of mine was
going back to his hometown

875
00:39:34,119 --> 00:39:35,599
and invited us over for a drink.

876
00:39:36,199 --> 00:39:37,440
I accidentally broke

877
00:39:37,559 --> 00:39:38,559
a teacup there.

878
00:39:39,239 --> 00:39:40,199
What teacup

879
00:39:40,559 --> 00:39:42,159
costs 150 taels of silver?

880
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:44,519
It's Chenghua doucai kiln!

881
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:46,320
That jade thumb ring

882
00:39:46,599 --> 00:39:47,840
was from mother.

883
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,719
The pawn deadline is coming up,

884
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:51,079
and I don't have money to redeem it.

885
00:39:51,679 --> 00:39:53,280
So I came to ask you for a loan.

886
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:55,039
Whatever it takes,

887
00:39:55,039 --> 00:39:56,320
I have to get it back.

888
00:39:59,039 --> 00:39:59,599
Really.

889
00:40:01,519 --> 00:40:02,239
Qingpu,

890
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:04,880
bring a 200 tael bank draft.

891
00:40:05,679 --> 00:40:07,159
Yes, Miss.

892
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:09,599
Thank you, Jinzhao!

893
00:40:24,679 --> 00:40:26,159
First a classmate's sister,

894
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,159
then an imperial kiln teacup.

895
00:40:28,559 --> 00:40:29,639
All nonsense.

896
00:40:31,079 --> 00:40:31,719
Qingpu,

897
00:40:32,039 --> 00:40:33,199
ask Mr. Ping to send two men

898
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:34,400
to watch him closely.

899
00:40:35,159 --> 00:40:36,239
I want to see

900
00:40:36,519 --> 00:40:37,719
what he's really doing.

901
00:40:38,199 --> 00:40:39,159
Yes, Miss.

902
00:40:52,719 --> 00:40:53,800
Watch out!

903
00:40:55,599 --> 00:40:56,480
What happened?

904
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,039
My lord,

905
00:40:58,239 --> 00:40:59,199
someone almost hit us.

906
00:41:00,719 --> 00:41:01,599
When did the capital

907
00:41:01,599 --> 00:41:02,760
get so polite?

908
00:41:03,079 --> 00:41:04,159
Not even a curse.

909
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:07,480
No wonder,

910
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:09,280
he's rushing off to gamble.

911
00:41:11,719 --> 00:41:12,840
A gambling house.

912
00:41:15,719 --> 00:41:16,679
No signboard?

913
00:41:17,079 --> 00:41:18,079
You don't know, my lord.

914
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:19,280
The more hidden it is,

915
00:41:19,519 --> 00:41:20,480
the bigger the business.

916
00:41:21,159 --> 00:41:22,480
It must have backing.

917
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:24,760
Whoever runs this
is really shady.

918
00:41:27,199 --> 00:41:27,760
Go.
Let's go, this way.

919
00:41:28,559 --> 00:41:29,119
It's near.

920
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,440
Masters, please come in.

921
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:31,400
[Good luck today.]

922
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,440
Gu Jinrong?

923
00:41:35,039 --> 00:41:35,880
Didn't expect him

924
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:36,960
to be a gambler.

925
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:39,280
Turns out he is.

926
00:41:40,159 --> 00:41:41,239
Wonder if Miss Gu

927
00:41:41,239 --> 00:41:42,400
knows about this.

928
00:41:43,039 --> 00:41:44,159
She definitely doesn't.

929
00:41:44,719 --> 00:41:45,760
Otherwise, with her temper,

930
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,480
she'd kill him.

931
00:41:51,519 --> 00:41:52,280
Let's go.

932
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:54,800
Go.

933
00:42:02,559 --> 00:42:03,320
So,

934
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:05,239
he's not gambling himself,

935
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,880
he's recruiting for the gambling house?

936
00:42:08,159 --> 00:42:08,960
Exactly.

937
00:42:09,119 --> 00:42:10,280
I saw it myself.

938
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:12,000
Mr. Jingrong didn't play,

939
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:13,920
he led those gamblers

940
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:14,840
into a private room.

941
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,039
So,

942
00:42:16,239 --> 00:42:17,840
he's working for the gambling house

943
00:42:18,320 --> 00:42:19,400
as a frontman.

944
00:42:19,719 --> 00:42:21,000
A frontman.

945
00:42:21,840 --> 00:42:22,760
Normally,

946
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,840
that should pay well.

947
00:42:24,199 --> 00:42:25,960
Then why does he still pawn things?

948
00:42:26,119 --> 00:42:27,079
Because that private room

949
00:42:27,079 --> 00:42:28,719
was rented by him.

950
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:30,079
Gambling house rules say,

951
00:42:30,079 --> 00:42:30,840
to lease a room,

952
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:32,440
one should pay three months upfront.

953
00:42:33,119 --> 00:42:34,599
Mr. Jingrong

954
00:42:34,599 --> 00:42:35,599
must be short on money,

955
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:36,880
that's why

956
00:42:37,079 --> 00:42:38,119
he pawned things.

957
00:42:39,679 --> 00:42:40,400
I see.

958
00:42:41,039 --> 00:42:43,159
This needs to be handled fast.

959
00:42:44,119 --> 00:42:46,000
Even if he doesn't gamble himself,

960
00:42:46,559 --> 00:42:47,880
luring others in is worse

961
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:50,280
than gambling himself.

962
00:42:54,239 --> 00:42:55,159
The Ministry of Rites

963
00:42:55,159 --> 00:42:56,599
sent the imperial exam pass list
for this round.

964
00:43:00,079 --> 00:43:00,679
Sir,

965
00:43:01,199 --> 00:43:02,920
people are talking outside,

966
00:43:03,840 --> 00:43:04,639
saying Mr. Xuanqing

967
00:43:04,639 --> 00:43:05,760
has your backing.

968
00:43:06,159 --> 00:43:07,079
He'll likely rank top

969
00:43:07,480 --> 00:43:08,559
in the palace exam.

970
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:10,400
Too much attention

971
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:12,000
may not be a good thing.

972
00:43:12,239 --> 00:43:12,880
Then,

973
00:43:13,639 --> 00:43:14,400
can we stop it?

974
00:43:14,719 --> 00:43:15,519
How can we?

975
00:43:17,800 --> 00:43:18,840
If His Majesty and my teacher

976
00:43:18,840 --> 00:43:20,000
both intend to promote him,

977
00:43:20,800 --> 00:43:21,880
how could I

978
00:43:22,119 --> 00:43:23,079
refuse their goodwill?

979
00:43:26,719 --> 00:43:27,480
Sir,

980
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:29,159
the Ji family sent gifts.

981
00:43:29,320 --> 00:43:30,000
Leave them there.

982
00:43:36,119 --> 00:43:37,360
According to Mr. Luo,

983
00:43:37,519 --> 00:43:39,159
these were personally chosen

984
00:43:39,159 --> 00:43:40,000
by Miss Gu.

985
00:43:40,079 --> 00:43:41,159
He said they were not enough

986
00:43:41,159 --> 00:43:42,599
to repay you for saving Miss Gu,

987
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:44,960
just a token of gratitude

988
00:43:45,400 --> 00:43:47,159
and to ease their own conscience.

989
00:43:48,360 --> 00:43:49,760
He's got a silver tongue.

990
00:43:53,880 --> 00:43:54,519
This is…

991
00:43:55,079 --> 00:43:56,199
A double-barreled telescope!

992
00:43:59,079 --> 00:44:00,079
Much clearer
than the single-tube one.

993
00:44:01,639 --> 00:44:03,119
The Ji family is wealthy.

994
00:44:03,519 --> 00:44:05,400
When Fujian opened trade back then,

995
00:44:05,400 --> 00:44:06,079
they also

996
00:44:06,079 --> 00:44:07,440
took a share of the profits.

997
00:44:08,280 --> 00:44:09,440
Half the Western goods

998
00:44:09,440 --> 00:44:10,880
you see in the capital now

999
00:44:11,239 --> 00:44:12,639
are brought in

1000
00:44:12,840 --> 00:44:14,360
by the Ji family's merchant ships.

1001
00:44:15,199 --> 00:44:16,679
Miss Gu really put thought into this.

1002
00:44:22,199 --> 00:44:22,880
What is this?

1003
00:44:23,320 --> 00:44:24,639
Looks like…

1004
00:44:24,960 --> 00:44:25,800
a pair of eyeglasses.

1005
00:44:26,079 --> 00:44:26,760
I've heard of them.

1006
00:44:27,119 --> 00:44:28,880
For people with poor eyesight, right?

1007
00:44:33,239 --> 00:44:35,199
Are you sure Mr. Luo said

1008
00:44:36,119 --> 00:44:37,199
these gifts were all

1009
00:44:37,199 --> 00:44:38,760
chosen by Miss Gu herself?

1010
00:44:39,159 --> 00:44:39,880
Yes.

1011
00:44:40,599 --> 00:44:41,920
They also said

1012
00:44:42,719 --> 00:44:44,639
those were things you could use.

1013
00:44:45,920 --> 00:44:46,760
Throw them all out.

1014
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:48,639
Yes.

1015
00:44:52,880 --> 00:44:53,800
Forget it.
